Ansible Deployer
================

Python script for ansible deployement.



Executing this script will
--------------------------

  - check if ansible is available (will show how to install if not)
  - create folowing directories :
     ~/ansible
        /tools
        /roles
        /playbooks

  - will download tools and roles (see ansible_deployer.cfg)



How to use
----------

 - edit ansible_deployer.cfg
 - execute ansible_deployer.py



